Amanda Jenkins has extensive commercial, educational and volunteer experien=
ce both in and outside the 3rd Sector. After completing her degree in Germa=
n, Amanda spent the next decade in the Lloyd's Insurance Market, followed b=
y senior roles with two New York law firms. She then moved to teaching Engl=
